OL,5, A safety investigation has warned that 
OL,6, young people with complex mental health
OL,7, needs are being put at significant     
OL,8, risk, by being placed on general       
OL,9, children's wards in England.           
OL,11,FThe findings come from the Healthcare  
OL,12,FSafety Investigation Branch (HSIB).    
OL,14,FBBC News recently highlighted the      
OL,15,Fplight of a 16-year-old autistic girl, 
OL,16,Fwho spent several months in a          
OL,17,Fchildren's ward.                       
OL,19,FOther families have since contacted the
OL,20,FBBC describing similar situations.     
